      <arrangement id="aspace_d142a7212bd3fa4d9d4a177652467dfa">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_9b03e31a13bef03f99acbb35f1e7bc1a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of student, subject, course, and seminar files documenting the activities and operations of the Yale Department of the History of Science and Medicine. Included are files of department chairmen Derek de Solla Price and Asger Aaboe.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_66eae0d4ec4e2705598faa108f0c524b">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
